{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">At Chroma Academy... Learn a craft. Harness magic. Discover your true calling. And maybe, save the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join the next generation of young wizards as they clean-up and combat hazardous environments and enemies, to restore balance in a land corrupted by poisonous fallout from an ancient magical battle between two feuding sorceress sisters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Features</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189890/extras/DescriptionImage_Match3.png?t=1730186839\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your match-3 combos determine your movement range, and your match-3 score dictates the damage you can inflict.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189890/extras/MatchAttackGIF.gif?t=1730186839\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189890/extras/DescriptionImage_Maps.png?t=1730186839\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No two runs are ever the same, offering a fresh experience with different rooms, enemies, and layouts each time you play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189890/extras/DescriptionImage_Items.png?t=1730186839\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create new character builds in every run by collecting various items that can significantly alter your character's progression and playstyle throughout the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">